body:
22-11-2016
My first steps back into coding.
Under the great and supportive supervision of my dear friend Marco (@McBeelen).
Today I created my GitHub page using the automatic generator. 
Just to find out how it works.
My goal is to code myself, and use as little generators as needed.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
